Accept: application/json
###

POST {{Catalog.Api_HostAddress}}/{{Catalog.Api_version}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop Stand",
  "description": "Aluminium adjustable stand",
  "price": 49.99
}
